    "legistation": "Section 365B(2)(b) of the Penal Code, as amended by Acts No. 22 of 1995, No. 29 of 1998, and No. 16 of 2006. - Section 154 of the Evidence Ordinance - Section 334(1) of the Code of Criminal Procedure Code Act No. 15 of 1979",
