 to bring it\n\nto the notice of the court any matter which if withheld may lead to a\n\nmiscarriage of justice\u2026\u2026\u2026\u201d\n\nIn Wijepala v The Attorney General [2001] 1 SLR 46 at pages 49 and 51"
