    "keywords": "Legitimate expectation (substantive & procedural) \u2022 Multi-Purpose Development Task Force recruitment policy \u2022 Contractual employees \u2022 Absorption/attachment \u2022 Cadre approval \u2022 Recruitment process \u2022 Mala fide in law",
    "legistation": "Article 140 of the Constitution of Sri Lanka",
