 \u20183R6a'), the DMS has, inter alia, sought to approve cadre, designate services for posts and directed compliance with the contents thereof. By virtue of the extension of the validity period of such approval, the approvals and directions contained therein continue in force, to date. Of particular significance to the instant case is the fact that the post of Provincial Director of Sports has been designated therein as a post reserved for the SLAS."
